{"tid":62072,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)happy new year","createTime":"2016-12-31T16:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T21:50:33.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"253087484e1c868404352aec23fb4eaf0e17dbdf","tid":62072,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T16:13:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wix.com/thanksyour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wix.com%2Fthanksyour&d=P08BAzofc8OAu%2FS17Cd%2BQnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=faadfc7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wix.com/thanksyour</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按右上分流A可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=P08BAzofc8OAu%2FS17Cd%2BQnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d933e5b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d7/%E6%B5%AA%E9%AD%8247.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd7%2F%25E6%25B5%25AA%25E9%25AD%258247.jpg&h=d1081cd0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/ac/Saving_Private_Ryan_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fac%2FSaving_Private_Ryan_poster.jpg&h=fe6817fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/o3J5ARkWZ_Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fo3J5ARkWZ_Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=01ca139a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.播磨國赤穗藩之主淺野長矩因受巫術影響而傷害吉良義央，其後被幕府將軍命令要求切腹謝罪。赤穗被廢藩並交由吉良義央看管，赤穗的武士亦在幕府將軍的命令下解散，成為浪人，身為筆頭家老的大石內藏助（真田廣之飾）更被吉良義央投入地牢。<br />\n一年後，大石內藏助獲釋。為報主公的仇，大石內藏助前往出島救出被賣為奴隸的魁（基努&middot;李維飾）並召集僅餘的家臣，一同前往吉良義央的所在地，以47人之力，誓要斬殺仇敵<br />\n<br />\n2.描述諾曼第登陸後，雷恩家4名於前線參戰的兒子中，3個兒子皆已於兩週內於海外各戰區陸續陣亡，其母親將在一天內接到三個兒子的死訊。而隸屬101空降師二等兵的小兒子詹姆斯&middot;法蘭西斯&middot;雷恩則在參與諾曼地的空降行動後下落不明，美國陸軍參謀長馬歇爾上將得知此事後出於人道考量，特令在法國前線作戰的美國陸軍遊騎兵組織一支8人小隊深入敵後，只為在人海茫茫、槍林彈雨中找出生死未卜的二等兵雷恩..<br />\n<br />\n3.黑幫大佬武藤為圓妻子的夢想，決定在她出獄前，為女兒美津子拍一部能當女主角的電影。可是，美津子卻與一個男人私奔，而武藤更與敵對勢力池上準備開戰，時間有限之下，武藤必需找一隊電影團隊。同時，自小希望能拍出一部驚天動地電影的平田，十年來一直鬱鬱不得志，誤打誤撞卻被美津子和武藤「賞識」，參與該電影的製作，沒想到，池上竟然對美津子也生了好感，決定參與這部電影。平田靈機一觸決定把兩派黑幫的殺戮場面拍成電影，於是，一班電影門外漢便能起攝影機，一邊拍片一邊殺戮．．．<br />\n<br />\n12 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d339d94f13230bb7e62e9f57bcf4c04f15d8c3c","tid":62072,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T16:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce3f7f0e03543d3027ea1bda49a9d82038f2717","tid":62072,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2faa4338a5f61138deeda36629512d629abb7584","tid":62072,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T17:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e009e3858267f5bc0a1c8e4205b17cdf33982e","tid":62072,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9186e691636d8df3420eb6acb585226f3e7a9d6c","tid":62072,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a